snippet.title: Bobls - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Bobls is a brand new difficult-but-charming precision platformer 
- Bounce and collect gems 
- Create your own levels
- Play a unique co-op campaign

Wishlist now on Steam: 
- https://store.steampowered.com/app/2459890/Bobls/

Follow Bedtime Digital Games:
